She walked up to Black Aracnia. "What is it that you would wish of 
me?" She wanted to fight.  She felt cheated out of a fight when the 
explosion put her down.  She wanted action, and wanted to see it soon.

She smiled to Aracnia,"Commander, what is it that you would have me 
do?"
